passages.name: TotalLoss
passages.text:
<Message>
  As your luggage has been lost for so long you might be able for compensation of all the lost items, you will be contacted by a claims handler in a few minutes.
</Message>

passages.name: NotYet
passages.text:
<Message>
  Your policy only gives you compensation for lost luggage after a minimum of 6 hours.
</Message>

<Message>
  You are welcome to report a claim after 6 hours have passed.
</Message>

passages.name: ClaimSubmitted
passages.text:
<Message>
  Thank you! We will contact you with more information shortly (usually within a few minutes)
</Message>

passages.name: Start
passages.text:
<Message>
  Sorry to hear about your delayed luggage.
</Message>

<Message>
  For how long has it been lost?
</Message>

<SelectAction>
  <Option>
    [[More than 6 hours->WhereDidYouGoFrom]]
  </Option>
  <Option>
    [[More than 30 days->TotalLoss]]
  </Option>
  <Option>
    [[Less than 6 hours->NotYet]]
  </Option>
</SelectAction>

passages.name: WhereDidYouGoFrom
passages.text:
<Message>
  Alright!
</Message>

<Message>
  To which city/airport did you travel?
</Message>

<TextAction placeholder="ex: Barcelona"
            key="from"
            next="[[Continue->ClaimSubmitted]]"
>
</TextAction>
